name: What light there is spins silver moons (iteration 4)
description:
This generative algorithm takes inspiration from a line in the poem "Hand in hand" by Irish poet Michelle O'Sullivan, from her collection "The blue end of stars". 

The algorithm represents my imagined experience of being amongst many moons playing along their near-terrestrial orbits - slivers between crescent and new.
